{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-319-bounded-sequences","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Zoezi la 319: Mfululizo ulio na mipaka","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Acha $x_1, x_2, \\ldots, x_n$ iwe mfululizo wa urefu $n$ unaokidhi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>$x_1 = 2$</li>\n<li>kwa kila $1 &#x3C; i ≤ n : x_{i - 1} &#x3C; x_i$</li>\n<li>kwa kila $i$ na $j$ zenye $1 ≤ i, j ≤ n : {(x_i)}^j &#x3C; {(x_j + 1)}^i$</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Postoji samo pet nizova dužine 2, odnosno: {2,4}, {2,5}, {2,6}, {2,7} i {2,8}. Postoje 293 niza dužine 5; tri primera su: {2,5,11,25,55}, {2,6,14,36,88}, {2,8,22,64,181}.</p>\n<p>Neka $t(n)$ bude broj takvih nizova dužine $n$. Dobijeno je da je $t(10) = 86195$ i $t(20) = 5227991891$.</p>\n<p>Tafuta $t({10}^{10})$ na toa jibu lako modulo $10^9$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4ab1000cf542c50ffbe","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301975,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-319-bounded-sequences"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function boundedSequences() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nboundedSequences();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>boundedSequences()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>268457129</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(boundedSequences(), 268457129);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-301-to-400","dashedName":"problem-319-bounded-sequences","certification":"project-euler","di